Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.55,0:08:09.55,ezc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海尼森行星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.55,0:08:09.55,eze,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Planet "Heinessen"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.55,0:08:09.55,ezj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惑星ハイネセン
